data.description: Welcome home to this two story home situated on corner lot that has sprinkler system and beautiful landscaping. As you walk into your new home it has a spacious foyer with high ceiling and open floorplan as you spend time with family and friends. Create memories with family/friend as you enjoy dinners in the formal dining room or eat in kitchen. Great room opens to kitchen with eat in area and spacious countertops with room for bar stools. Your guest can enjoy the guest bedroom down stair with full bath. Master bedroom and 3 more bedrooms upstairs with a bonus/media room. Spend the evening outback in the screen porch, in the hot tub, or by the custom fire pit.
